Insider Activity


Individual




Frank Henry Brod



Mr. Frank H. Brod, CPA, is CAO, Vice President-Finance & Administration at Microsoft Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Financial Accounting Foundation.
Mr. Brod was previously employed as Vice President & Controller by The Dow Chemical Co. and Vice President & Controller by Union Carbide Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from the Illinois Institute of Technology.



