Frank H. Brod Bio


















   
Financial Accounting Foundation
Frank H. Brod
Secretary and Treasurer
Board of Trustees

Frank Brod is Corporate Vice President, Finance and Administration, and Chief Accounting Officer at Microsoft Corporation. Mr. Brod joined the Board of Trustees in January 2008, and was nominated by Financial Executives International (FEI). He serves on the FAF’s Finance and Compensation committee.
  











